name: Evolve FANGMA Index ETF
longDescription: The Evolve FANGMA Index ETF (the Fund) seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive FANGMA Equal Weight Index Canadian Dollar Hedged, or any successor thereto. The Fund invests in equity securities of Alphabet Inc., Amazon Inc., Apple Inc., Facebook Inc., Netflix Inc. and Microsoft Corp.
